        crm:P3_has_note               "Detached mural painting (fresco) by Alessandro Botticelli, depicting Saint Augustine in his study. The work is currently held at the Opificio delle Pietre Dure, Florence. It was the subject of a synchronized VIS-NIR reflectance imaging spectroscopy and 3D laser scanning campaign aimed at characterising the painted surface and demonstrating the performance of georeferenced multi-sensor acquisition."@en ;
